{"tid":316281,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"就係今日..我發現阿head嘅一個秘密...","createTime":"2017-07-10T15:15:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-11T15:35:10.000Z","uid":120540,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5df26e6b3ff8be158155bc23cae64f61b48bd3ca","tid":316281,"uid":120540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T15:15:12.000Z","msg":"今日同阿head早機飛到來東京公幹<br />\n跟住就係酒店check in完<br />\n唉&hellip;諗到來緊幾晚要同呢條友訓埋同一間房<br />\n就咩mood都無曬<br />\n廢話唔多講，我發現他做左一件好恐怖的事<br />\n話說我去沖涼啦<br />\n咪係喼度巢翻衫褲出來就入左去沖啦<br />\n沖完出來的時候<br />\n見到阿head面色有d古怪坐住系度<br />\n問他咩嘢又話無嘢<br />\n之後我就發現行李喼嘅衫亂左<br />\n坐住睇下聽日行程的時候<br />\n阿head就話乜你喜歡著三角深色底褲架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住就同我講他自己喜歡有花紋淺粉色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點算啊<br />\n我今晚仲要同佢共宿一宵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇連登仔係附近可以救下我？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21992be28edae2bde5b4b5e98a620f1a8b669207","tid":316281,"uid":82142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T15:16:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa7b8bd468b090c6e0da5dcecf07e63f81da0c21","tid":316281,"uid":47478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T15:17:52.000Z","msg":"上位機會"},{"pid":"92c5a9f0b9ea0314f402e262bde9c7f7ee25c2ee","tid":316281,"uid":63515,"like":0,"d